The story of Rolex is not about Rolex, but about the development of watches from pocket watches to their current form, which was made possible thanks to the imagination and determination of a young German orphan, who defied the factors of racism in Britain, carefully understood the market mechanisms, developed exceptional watches and marketed them greatly: the story of “Hans Wilsdorf.” Founder of the largest Swiss watch company in the world: Rolex. I don't mind if you give me a Rolex watch :)
Thanks Rolex.
